  "3270820": {
    "name": "空岛立方",
    "steam_appid": 3270820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/c0fffd604b82b29492d9d66ef7a01c94.avif?t=1744958238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras_big/c0fffd604b82b29492d9d66ef7a01c94.avif?t=1744958238 width=800 height=358 /></span>《空岛立方》是一款3D方块消除游戏。每一个数字，都是智慧的角力。每一次敲击，都是创造力的释放。每一个作品的雕琢过程，都是艺术对心灵的洗礼。揭开隐藏在色彩斑斓方块背后的神秘图形，探索造型艺术的无限可能！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-探索结构</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索由蓝色完整方块与粉色不规则方块构成的奇妙结构。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f590c572417a4fc48b46b0206dcf085d.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f590c572417a4fc48b46b0206dcf085d.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f590c572417a4fc48b46b0206dcf085d.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-数字谜题</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意外立面数字，它们是水平、垂直、纵深3个方向上方块的谜底。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/df17081cfa37759408ba074c2f624087.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/df17081cfa37759408ba074c2f624087.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/df17081cfa37759408ba074c2f624087.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-成功在即</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当方块内被包裹的事物逐渐显露，你将知道成功近在咫尺。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/6be29476e15e37029d89e8c99a3b101c.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/6be29476e15e37029d89e8c99a3b101c.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/6be29476e15e37029d89e8c99a3b101c.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-温柔致敬</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《空岛立方》中，每一处细节都是对美好生活的温柔致敬。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/e79a43cf467535d3cc2278875bb93a59.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/e79a43cf467535d3cc2278875bb93a59.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/e79a43cf467535d3cc2278875bb93a59.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-梦幻光影</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的艺术家们精心调配了每一抹色彩，让光影在立方体上跳跃，营造出一个既真实又梦幻的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从细腻的纹理到流畅的动画，每个方块都仿佛在呼吸，每一次点击都能感受到它们的生命力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从小桥流水的宁静致远到田园牧歌的悠然自得，从大雪皑皑张灯结彩到天涯海角风急浪高。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/f8002c7e0f89448ec384a15fabb0d3ae.avif?t=1744958238\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras_big/f8002c7e0f89448ec384a15fabb0d3ae.avif?t=1744958238 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >-生活画卷</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一座座小小的空岛，是你我心底对于可能拥有的生活一帧帧美好的描画，是我们在日复一日习以为常之外还想要度过的一种种人生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/4e755fa81e278e5172744582d8b05222.poster.avif?t=1744958238\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/4e755fa81e278e5172744582d8b05222.webm?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270820/extras/4e755fa81e278e5172744582d8b05222.mp4?t=1744958238\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前已经开放DEMO测试环节</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您在游玩中有什么建议</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎联系我们~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群：397920805</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><a href=\"mailto:邮箱：3941637341@qq.com\">邮箱：3941637341@qq.com</a></p>",
